title: Hamilton Beach Sure-Crisp Air Fryer Toaster Oven Combo, Fits 9” Pizza, 4 Slice Capacity, Powerful Circulation, Auto Shutoff, Stainless Steel (31403)
description: The Hamilton Beach® Sure-Crisp™ Air Fryer Toaster Oven creates evenly browned, crispy foods with Sure-Crisp air frying functionality. The 4 versatile settings let you air fry, toast, bake or broil a wide variety of food and it has a 4 slice capacity.
